WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
ظآزThat dayظآز

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
ظآزNothing stays together foreverظآز

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
ظآزI've quit romanceظآز

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
ظآزWho hasn't failed againظآز

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
ظآزCrying in deathظآز

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
ظآزAnd in lifeظآز

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
ظآزEven nowظآز

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
ظآزWe keep learningظآز

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
ظآزIt's no surpriseظآز

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
ظآزBeing happy is so hardظآز

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
ظآزWeirdly, I became a role modelظآز

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
ظآزOn the day we met again, we said hiظآز

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
ظآزIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintظآز

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
ظآزWho can do anything without regretظآز

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
ظآزI am all rightظآز

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
ظآزMay you live in peaceظآز

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
ظآزLet the world roarظآز

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
ظآزSounds like a carnivalظآز

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
ظآزBeing alive is never dullظآز

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
ظآزHow wonderful to be freeظآز

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
ظآزI became even better without youظآز

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
ظآزNothing can be perfectظآز

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
ظآزWe bless each other in painظآز

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
ظآزWe nod and smileظآز

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
ظآزMay we both be wellظآز

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:44.018
=Episode 15=

01:44.176 --> 01:45.816
One million six hundred thousand.

01:46.096 --> 01:47.256
Going once.

01:47.816 --> 01:49.256
One million six hundred thousand.

01:49.616 --> 01:50.976
Going twice.

01:57.976 --> 01:58.655
Three million.

01:59.176 --> 02:00.215
Three million?

02:01.456 --> 02:02.536
Three million?

02:02.536 --> 02:03.575
That's a lot.

02:08.215 --> 02:09.136
Three million.

02:09.416 --> 02:10.736
Any higher bids?

02:10.775 --> 02:11.856
Final call then.

02:12.136 --> 02:13.616
Three million. Going once.

02:14.215 --> 02:15.056
Three million.

02:15.296 --> 02:16.136
Going twice.

02:17.016 --> 02:17.775
Three million.

02:18.336 --> 02:19.416
Third call.

02:20.336 --> 02:21.056
Sold!

02:26.576 --> 02:27.176
Are you happy?

02:28.775 --> 02:29.535
Try it on.

02:29.736 --> 02:30.136
Okay.

02:30.136 --> 02:30.576
Okay.

02:30.576 --> 02:33.215
Next, let me introduce
our second auction item.

02:34.456 --> 02:37.016
Qinghua porcelain vase
with dragon and lotus motifs.

02:37.375 --> 02:39.176
As you can see here.

02:39.255 --> 02:41.176
It features elegant shaping
and fluid lines.

02:41.456 --> 02:42.815
With centuries of history,

02:42.815 --> 02:44.056
it remains well-preserved.

02:49.576 --> 02:50.176
Lei.

02:53.616 --> 02:54.375
Does it look good?

02:57.456 --> 02:58.176
Quite exquisite.

03:00.416 --> 03:01.016
You like it?

03:05.215 --> 03:06.336
I can't give you this one.

03:10.095 --> 03:12.495
But this one is fine.

03:17.056 --> 03:17.576
No need.

03:17.975 --> 03:18.456
Don't move.

03:19.136 --> 03:20.176
Auctions

03:20.456 --> 03:22.655
are just excuses for show.

03:23.495 --> 03:24.975
Charity's the real purpose.

03:25.695 --> 03:26.640
Kindness matters most.

03:27.456 --> 03:28.495
That's why you won't find

03:28.655 --> 03:29.935
real treasures here.

03:34.416 --> 03:35.775
You think it's worth three mil?

03:38.695 --> 03:39.655
Take it if you like it.

03:42.296 --> 03:43.935
It suits you.

03:44.416 --> 03:45.176
Isn't it lovely?

03:46.176 --> 03:47.215
So beautiful.

03:47.935 --> 03:49.016
It was made for you.

03:49.695 --> 03:50.456
It's yours now.

03:51.416 --> 03:52.016
Let's go, dear.

03:54.215 --> 03:54.935
What a trinket.

03:56.616 --> 03:57.552
What else do you like?

03:58.224 --> 03:59.408
I'll bid for it next round.

03:59.935 --> 04:01.016
Know your limits.

04:01.695 --> 04:02.495
Be gracious.

04:03.016 --> 04:03.655
You said it.

04:04.136 --> 04:04.935
Remember to smile.

04:05.576 --> 04:06.215
Ms. Xu, hello.

04:06.215 --> 04:06.815
Mr. Shen.

04:06.815 --> 04:07.815
What an enviable couple.

04:09.095 --> 04:09.935
So beautiful.

04:10.215 --> 04:11.215
Hello, Ms. Xu.

04:11.655 --> 04:12.255
Mr. Shen.

04:17.255 --> 04:19.736
Good evening, viewers across the nation.

04:20.176 --> 04:23.176
Welcome to Financial News.
I'm host Xu Yan.

04:24.176 --> 04:28.375
Groundbreaking ceremony of Jinda Group's
Huanyu International real estate project

04:28.616 --> 04:30.216
successfully concluded today.

04:30.416 --> 04:33.776
This 300,000 square meter development

04:33.895 --> 04:35.335
features not only luxury residences,

04:35.495 --> 04:37.656
but also international-grade
office towers

04:37.776 --> 04:39.056
and premium shopping complexes.

04:39.296 --> 04:42.015
It's crowned as Jinda Group's
flagship endeavor.

04:43.135 --> 04:44.375
(Good evening, everyone.)

04:44.375 --> 04:46.216
(This is Entertainment Frontline.)

04:46.375 --> 04:49.375
(At Jinda Group's recent
groundbreaking event,)

04:49.375 --> 04:51.096
(we met picture-perfect newlyweds.)

04:51.416 --> 04:52.736
(They sweetened our screens.)

04:52.815 --> 04:54.255
(Shen Haoming, Xu Yan, a couple's quiz)
(Sugar overload warning!)

04:54.935 --> 04:56.455
(You maintain such marital bliss.)

04:56.495 --> 04:57.616
(Any secret formula?)

04:57.616 --> 04:58.895
(Share with our audience.)

05:05.255 --> 05:06.616
(No secrets here,)

05:07.416 --> 05:09.856
(just good fortune.)

05:10.856 --> 05:11.695
(Then comes)

05:12.056 --> 05:15.695
(mutual admiration between partners.)

05:16.296 --> 05:17.736
(I respect her capabilities,)

05:18.216 --> 05:19.736
(but most commendable is that)

05:20.135 --> 05:23.495
(despite having easier career options)

05:23.976 --> 05:25.495
(or even choosing domestic life,)

05:26.495 --> 05:29.695
(she pursued her childhood dream.)

05:45.096 --> 05:46.736
Yan, your tea.

05:48.296 --> 05:52.296
First time seeing a host report
on her own husband's business.

05:52.495 --> 05:54.216
You two look perfect together,

05:54.335 --> 05:55.815
just like a match made in heaven.

05:56.255 --> 05:57.935
Your husband clearly adores you.

06:02.015 --> 06:03.976
Yan, are you tired?

06:07.335 --> 06:08.695
Take a breather then.

06:08.935 --> 06:10.135
I'll monitor the edits.

06:11.736 --> 06:13.096
Call me anytime.

06:38.192 --> 06:40.123
ظآزYou once shone like the sunظآز

06:40.123 --> 06:43.202
ظآزThe flowers bloomed and witheredظآز

06:44.656 --> 06:46.416
ظآزOur palms connected when we held handsظآز

06:46.416 --> 06:49.423
ظآزThen tangled into waitingظآز

06:51.312 --> 06:53.210
ظآزWe've lost those beautiful momentsظآز

06:53.250 --> 06:56.442
ظآزThey passed by countless timesظآز

06:57.104 --> 06:59.056
ظآزI couldn't embrace that feelingظآز

06:59.056 --> 07:03.049
ظآزMy love solidifies into amberظآز

07:04.272 --> 07:06.352
ظآزWhen you speak, the universe haltsظآز

07:06.352 --> 07:09.232
ظآزEven fate grows stillظآز

07:10.032 --> 07:13.200
ظآزSunset glow caressesظآز

07:13.200 --> 07:16.481
ظآزYour silhouetteظآز

07:17.328 --> 07:19.472
ظآزTill sunset takes dreams awayظآز

07:19.472 --> 07:22.192
ظآزLeaving me, unbrokenظآز

07:23.216 --> 07:25.449
ظآزEnvying dustظآز

07:25.968 --> 07:29.332
ظآزResting in your heartظآز

07:30.512 --> 07:32.428
ظآزLike fireworks that lovedظآز

07:32.428 --> 07:34.087
ظآزRushing toward the starsظآز

07:34.087 --> 07:36.146
ظآزUndaunted by painظآز

07:36.989 --> 07:38.890
ظآزFearless of flamesظآز

07:38.890 --> 07:42.544
ظآزEven if just a fleeting sparkleظآز

07:43.549 --> 07:45.373
ظآزWe shed tearsظآز

07:45.469 --> 07:49.221
ظآزDeep blue seas turn to foamظآز

07:49.221 --> 07:53.072
ظآزWe regained freedomظآز

07:53.072 --> 07:55.801
ظآزIf you remember meظآز

07:55.801 --> 07:59.152
ظآزThen I'm pleasedظآز

08:10.127 --> 08:28.947
(Grandma calling)

08:30.575 --> 08:31.255
Hello, Grandma.

08:33.615 --> 08:34.416
Yan,

08:35.056 --> 08:36.855
how have you been lately?

08:40.695 --> 08:42.056
Why do you ask?

08:44.815 --> 08:45.656
Nothing.

08:46.335 --> 08:51.296
I just saw you on TV.
You looked a bit unhappy.

08:52.575 --> 08:56.215
I'm just worried you're going
through some trouble.

09:01.376 --> 09:03.056
If I'm overthinking it...

09:04.575 --> 09:06.176
I'm glad you're okay.

09:06.256 --> 09:07.615
Good that you're okay.

09:14.296 --> 09:15.136
(Yan)
Everything is fine.

09:15.735 --> 09:16.656
Don't worry.

09:18.256 --> 09:18.855
Okay.

09:19.575 --> 09:20.416
That's good.

09:21.896 --> 09:22.935
Yan,

09:24.335 --> 09:28.656
you've had such a tough journey
building your career.

09:29.776 --> 09:32.296
Now that you've found a job you love,

09:33.496 --> 09:34.896
you must cherish it.

09:36.416 --> 09:38.335
Whether it's work

09:38.416 --> 09:39.896
or personal life,

09:40.256 --> 09:41.695
be down-to-earth.

09:42.056 --> 09:43.016
As for me,

09:43.536 --> 09:44.695
I'm getting old.

09:45.735 --> 09:51.095
I won't be around much longer, right?

09:51.815 --> 09:53.455
Don't talk like that.

09:57.656 --> 09:59.935
I'll take leave next week

10:00.176 --> 10:01.615
and spend more days with you,

10:01.896 --> 10:02.496
okay?

10:03.975 --> 10:05.776
No need, really.

10:06.296 --> 10:07.575
If you have time for a vacation,

10:07.735 --> 10:09.095
find a nice place

10:09.416 --> 10:12.575
and travel with Haoming.
That'd be lovely!

10:13.815 --> 10:15.776
Take lots of photos to show me.

10:15.975 --> 10:18.016
I'd be so happy.

10:20.095 --> 10:23.095
We have plenty of time together.

10:27.776 --> 10:29.455
I just miss you.

10:33.615 --> 10:34.695
I want to come home.

10:38.056 --> 10:39.855
I miss you too.

10:46.776 --> 10:50.776
Do you want to have a child?

10:52.176 --> 10:56.215
I want a great-grandchild.

12:29.575 --> 12:30.136
Grandma.

12:35.896 --> 12:36.656
Grandma!

12:40.296 --> 12:41.095
Grandma!

12:51.536 --> 12:52.256
Yan,

12:52.536 --> 12:53.935
- you're finally back!
- Hello, madam.

12:54.256 --> 12:56.016
Your grandma fainted last night.

12:56.256 --> 12:58.256
We rushed her to the county hospital.

12:59.896 --> 13:00.615
County hospital?

13:01.376 --> 13:02.695
Your parents went too.

13:15.536 --> 13:16.095
Yan,

13:16.416 --> 13:16.935
you're here.

13:16.975 --> 13:18.016
Check on Grandma.

13:19.776 --> 13:20.376
Grandma.

13:24.815 --> 13:25.496
Grandma.

13:25.896 --> 13:26.335
Yan.

13:26.855 --> 13:27.376
Yan,

13:28.335 --> 13:29.215
don't worry.

13:30.215 --> 13:31.056
The doctor said

13:31.296 --> 13:33.575
she had transient cerebral ischemia.

13:34.016 --> 13:35.615
Luckily, we brought her in time.

13:36.335 --> 13:37.416
She's stable now.

13:37.975 --> 13:39.016
She'll be fine.

13:43.136 --> 13:44.296
When will she wake up?

13:45.656 --> 13:47.016
She's just weak,

13:47.335 --> 13:48.656
and needs rest now.

13:58.176 --> 13:58.935
You can go home.

13:59.136 --> 13:59.855
I'll stay.

14:00.536 --> 14:02.095
Let's all stay together.

14:04.416 --> 14:05.296
I'll be fine here.

14:14.896 --> 14:15.335
Okay.

14:15.776 --> 14:17.776
We'll relieve you tomorrow morning.

14:24.575 --> 14:25.656
If anything happens,

14:25.815 --> 14:27.095
call us, okay?

14:56.496 --> 15:00.735
(At this moment, I decided
to divorce Shen Haoming.)

15:03.176 --> 15:04.656
(If not for maintaining lies,)

15:05.656 --> 15:07.496
(Grandma could've seen me
in a wedding dress.)

15:08.695 --> 15:10.136
(If not for maintaining lies,)

15:10.776 --> 15:12.575
(Grandma should've been by my side,)

15:12.855 --> 15:14.896
(rather than collapsing
alone and helpless.)

15:16.776 --> 15:19.136
(My only chance to make amends)

15:20.176 --> 15:23.815
(is to completely end the lies myself.)

15:48.496 --> 15:49.735
Who told you to come back?

15:55.296 --> 15:56.095
You're awake.

15:57.656 --> 15:58.575
Still feeling unwell?

16:02.215 --> 16:03.056
Have some water.

16:05.776 --> 16:06.256
Come on.

16:06.776 --> 16:07.536
Small sips.

16:09.056 --> 16:09.735
Small sips.

16:11.975 --> 16:12.776
Don't choke on it.

16:18.735 --> 16:19.855
Are you feeling okay?

16:20.615 --> 16:21.256
Yes.

16:22.176 --> 16:22.935
Yan,

16:23.975 --> 16:26.176
raise my bed a bit straighter.

16:26.455 --> 16:27.815
Why? It's the middle of the night.

16:27.815 --> 16:28.575
Just sleep.

16:29.335 --> 16:29.935
Just do it.

16:39.896 --> 16:40.855
- It's okay.
- Okay?

16:41.095 --> 16:42.056
Okay.

16:49.455 --> 16:50.256
Yan.

16:52.656 --> 16:53.975
Something's bothering you.

16:55.776 --> 16:57.136
Tell me about it.

17:01.935 --> 17:03.256
Come back to Jingzhou with me.

17:06.736 --> 17:07.655
Once you're discharged,

17:07.655 --> 17:09.135
we'll go pack your things, okay?

17:10.296 --> 17:12.855
I've lived in the countryside
my whole life,

17:13.696 --> 17:16.536
and I enjoy the peaceful life here.

17:17.175 --> 17:18.175
I know.

17:18.776 --> 17:20.095
So I've thought it through.

17:20.615 --> 17:23.135
We can rent a place with a small yard

17:23.496 --> 17:25.095
in the suburbs of Jingzhou.

17:25.536 --> 17:27.575
You can grow flowers and plants there,

17:27.655 --> 17:29.415
just like you do now. How's that?

17:31.016 --> 17:33.415
That does sound nice.

17:34.375 --> 17:37.736
I know you're worried about me,

17:39.496 --> 17:43.736
but working alone in the city
must be so hard for you.

17:44.056 --> 17:48.936
I just want you
to live your own life well.

17:50.175 --> 17:53.615
Your happiness is my happiness.

18:00.776 --> 18:02.415
I'm doing fine.

18:02.696 --> 18:03.736
Don't worry about me.

18:05.296 --> 18:10.216
Folks like us from the countryside

18:10.976 --> 18:13.175
are used to living in old houses

18:13.855 --> 18:15.456
and doing farm work.

18:16.335 --> 18:18.615
Suddenly moving away

18:19.056 --> 18:19.655
and settling

18:20.415 --> 18:22.855
into a big city house

18:24.135 --> 18:25.575
would leave me feeling lost.

18:26.016 --> 18:28.976
My whole being would feel uneasy.

18:31.135 --> 18:31.936
Got it.

18:34.135 --> 18:35.655
I'll sleep now. You should leave.

18:59.456 --> 18:59.895
Mr. Shen,

19:00.016 --> 19:02.135
the legal risk report
requires your signature.

19:07.936 --> 19:08.536
Mr. Shen,

19:09.095 --> 19:11.976
I have some information about your wife.

19:12.855 --> 19:13.415
Go on.

19:14.095 --> 19:15.655
She is looking for a divorce lawyer.

19:17.375 --> 19:18.335
She won't divorce me.

19:20.095 --> 19:23.016
I recommend making early preparations,

19:23.415 --> 19:24.175
just in case.

19:24.575 --> 19:26.448
Now's critical for her job confirmation.

19:27.095 --> 19:28.175
She's worked so hard

19:28.415 --> 19:29.496
for that position.

19:30.296 --> 19:31.655
She won't give it up now.

19:31.776 --> 19:33.855
Nor will she abandon
everything she's achieved.

19:37.520 --> 19:38.286
(Shen Haoming)

20:04.656 --> 20:06.591
(Divorce Agreement)

20:08.095 --> 20:08.976
Let's get divorced.

20:13.095 --> 20:15.256
Didn't we clarify everything last time?

20:15.855 --> 20:16.736
What do you want now?

20:16.815 --> 20:18.095
I'll leave with nothing,

20:20.736 --> 20:21.895
not taking a cent from you.

20:28.296 --> 20:29.655
Xu Yan, you know very well

20:30.855 --> 20:33.375
that once we divorce, the luxury cars,

20:33.976 --> 20:34.536
mansions,

20:34.976 --> 20:35.696
chauffeurs,

20:35.855 --> 20:36.415
maids,

20:36.855 --> 20:37.456
designer goods,

20:38.095 --> 20:40.415
and all Shen family resources

20:40.696 --> 20:41.815
will be stripped from you.

20:41.936 --> 20:43.216
They were never truly mine.

20:45.976 --> 20:47.296
And I don't need them anymore.

20:52.895 --> 20:55.175
Or do you think
now that you have your career

20:57.256 --> 20:59.415
and that host position within reach,

21:00.335 --> 21:01.736
you can afford to be reckless?

21:07.095 --> 21:07.815
Mr. Zhou,

21:09.496 --> 21:10.696
as we previously agreed,

21:10.855 --> 21:11.536
my sponsorship

21:11.976 --> 21:12.696
will be postponed.

21:16.296 --> 21:17.256
Should I send it?

21:35.120 --> 21:39.216
(Fang Lei)

21:39.312 --> 21:40.216
(Audio Recording)

21:40.216 --> 21:41.016
What do you want?

21:45.855 --> 21:46.415
Fang Lei,

21:47.696 --> 21:49.615
I'm warning you
to stop harassing my husband.

21:49.615 --> 21:50.536
(Cancel)

21:50.536 --> 21:51.936
If you have any dignity,

21:52.855 --> 21:54.456
disappear from our lives.

21:55.095 --> 21:56.256
Who are you to order me?

21:57.976 --> 21:58.895
I put the past down

22:00.256 --> 22:01.776
to your youth and immaturity.

22:03.855 --> 22:05.615
But if you keep this up,

22:06.655 --> 22:08.696
you're deliberately
destroying a marriage.

22:13.855 --> 22:15.575
If your parents also have any dignity,

22:17.175 --> 22:18.335
I advise you to stop.

22:18.736 --> 22:19.496
Is that a threat?

22:19.815 --> 22:22.655
(Fang Lei)
Xu Yan, let me be frank with you.

22:23.056 --> 22:26.095
I returned just to be with Haoming.

22:26.296 --> 22:28.696
I don't care if he's married.

22:28.976 --> 22:31.175
I made myself clear last time.

22:31.415 --> 22:33.536
Haochen is Haoming's son,

22:33.776 --> 22:35.855
and I'm Haochen's aunt.

22:36.415 --> 22:38.056
I've already won this battle.

22:38.456 --> 22:40.736
(End)
The one clinging to the Shen family...

22:41.855 --> 22:45.575
Do you want an amicable divorce,
or a fight to the bitter end?

22:47.575 --> 22:48.536
The choice is yours.

22:57.808 --> 23:04.432
ظآزMisplaced glory is just danger's omenظآز

23:05.135 --> 23:06.615
I'll come collect my things soon.

23:07.736 --> 23:08.655
Where will you move?

23:10.375 --> 23:12.016
There are divorce procedures

23:12.736 --> 23:14.936
and documents requiring your signature.

23:15.175 --> 23:16.375
I'll text you the address.

23:16.815 --> 23:18.016
Ten o'clock on the 8th,

23:21.135 --> 23:22.288
at the Civil Affairs Bureau.

23:24.880 --> 23:29.104
ظآزForgive myselfظآز

23:29.104 --> 23:31.024
ظآزWhat kind of meظآز

23:31.024 --> 23:32.624
ظآزIs the best meظآز

23:32.944 --> 23:34.640
ظآزWho defines itظآز

23:36.816 --> 23:38.512
ظآزWhat kind of meظآز

23:38.768 --> 23:40.432
ظآزIs the best meظآز

23:40.624 --> 23:42.832
