27:48.016 --> 27:49.895
So failure isn't an option here.

27:50.175 --> 27:52.575
Otherwise, the malpractice fallout
alone will ruin you.

27:54.056 --> 27:54.976
Understood, sir.

27:55.815 --> 27:56.776
Get some good rest.

28:40.135 --> 28:41.335
What are you doing?

28:41.615 --> 28:42.335
Stress relief.

28:48.895 --> 28:50.575
