30:44.776 --> 30:45.256
Hello.

30:46.056 --> 30:48.135
Ms. Xu, I haven't seen you in ages.

30:48.375 --> 30:49.736
What service would you like today?

30:49.976 --> 30:51.575
Your favorite masseuse is available.

30:51.575 --> 30:52.815
I'll have her come down.

30:53.392 --> 30:55.312
- No.3, come down.
- Can I cancel my membership?

30:57.615 --> 30:58.375
Ms. Xu,

30:58.536 --> 31:00.256
was our service unsatisfactory?

31:00.335 --> 31:02.256
You're not switching
to our competitor, are you?

31:02.696 --> 31:03.536
Ms. Xu,

31:03.615 --> 31:05.256
please share any complaints.

31:05.335 --> 31:05.736
We'll...

31:05.976 --> 31:07.496
Just process the refund, please.

31:08.976 --> 31:10.175
Okay. Come with me.

31:10.175 --> 31:10.696
Thank you.

31:19.776 --> 31:20.655
Ms. Xu,

31:20.736 --> 31:22.056
your refund is processed.

31:22.536 --> 31:23.135
Thanks.

31:28.936 --> 31:29.696
Excuse me,

31:30.415 --> 31:32.655
I didn't get the refund notification.

31:32.776 --> 31:34.575
Could you double-check?

31:35.952 --> 31:37.712
Refunds go back the same way
they were paid.

31:37.776 --> 31:40.095
Your husband opened
this account with you.

31:43.976 --> 31:44.895
Now I remember.

31:47.056 --> 31:47.696
Thanks.

31:53.335 --> 31:54.095
(Hengyue Law Firm)
That guy

31:54.175 --> 31:55.655
is 19 years younger than my mom.

31:55.976 --> 31:57.335
At first, he sweet-talked my mom

31:57.375 --> 31:58.575
to buy him houses and cars.

31:58.615 --> 31:58.976
Alright.

31:59.175 --> 32:01.615
After succeeding, he started
coveting our family's shares.

32:02.135 --> 32:04.456
This young wolf sure knows his tricks.

32:05.256 --> 32:07.696
My mom's currently blinded by passion.

32:07.696 --> 32:08.976
But I won't stand for it.

32:09.175 --> 32:11.655
I need to protect my own interests.

32:12.095 --> 32:12.815
Mr. Qiu,

32:12.976 --> 32:14.615
regarding my portion of the assets,

32:14.655 --> 32:15.615
what should I do?

32:15.936 --> 32:16.575
We've noted

32:16.575 --> 32:17.496
your requests.

32:17.736 --> 32:20.415
We'll draft the contract
and email it to you by tomorrow.

32:20.575 --> 32:22.256
We can talk again if there's a problem.

32:22.375 --> 32:23.776
I have three strategies.

32:29.056 --> 32:30.335
Is that man earlier

32:30.415 --> 32:31.536
a lawyer?

32:32.016 --> 32:32.696
Mr. Ding

32:32.855 --> 32:33.895
specializes in divorce.

32:34.135 --> 32:35.496
He's famous in legal circles.

32:35.696 --> 32:37.216
He handles only top-tier clients.

32:37.855 --> 32:39.135
Divorce lawyer?

32:52.095 --> 32:53.776
Did Yan's
field interview schedule change?

32:53.855 --> 32:54.976
I haven't heard anything.

32:55.855 --> 32:57.296
Yan is not just asking for leave,

32:57.536 --> 32:59.056
she's asking for an extended leave.

32:59.615 --> 33:00.615
You didn't know that?

33:00.936 --> 33:03.216
Why would she take an extended leave
all of a sudden?

33:03.855 --> 33:06.175
Could it be some big news

33:06.536 --> 33:07.335
about a baby?

33:07.976 --> 33:10.216
I heard she's getting divorced.

33:11.175 --> 33:12.415
Could there be an affair?

33:12.936 --> 33:14.175
I really don't know.

33:14.936 --> 33:16.256
I said nothing.

33:32.776 --> 33:33.456
Come in.

33:36.016 --> 33:36.696
Haoming.

33:39.696 --> 33:40.415
Where's Mr. Fang?

33:41.375 --> 33:43.256
I had my father's secretary
tell you this.

33:45.415 --> 33:46.056
Haoming,

33:46.375 --> 33:46.976
Haoming.

33:48.095 --> 33:49.655
Don't you always keep things business?

33:49.855 --> 33:50.216
Okay.

33:50.415 --> 33:51.736
Let's discuss business then.

33:52.095 --> 33:54.415
My father and I contributed
to the New District project.

33:54.696 --> 33:56.696
A business dinner
isn't unreasonable, right?

33:57.456 --> 33:59.056
Is this really necessary?

34:00.016 --> 34:01.056
I heard you're divorcing.

34:06.855 --> 34:07.815
It seems true.

34:09.135 --> 34:11.295
I heard she hired a lawyer.

34:14.135 --> 34:14.896
I knew it.

34:14.936 --> 34:16.056
Someone like her

34:16.416 --> 34:18.255
only pretends to love you.

34:18.615 --> 34:20.135
Once realizing she can't control you,

34:20.135 --> 34:21.376
she finds escape routes,

34:21.496 --> 34:22.416
maximizing her gains.

34:23.456 --> 34:24.175
Haoming.

34:24.735 --> 34:25.255
Yan,

34:25.520 --> 34:27.655
the interview's in the executive lounge
on this floor.

34:28.135 --> 34:29.175
The guest will come

34:29.175 --> 34:30.175
after makeup.

34:34.735 --> 34:36.336
When will you see clearly?

34:36.416 --> 34:38.095
I'm the one who truly loves you.

35:36.695 --> 35:38.016
Before my divorce,

35:39.135 --> 35:40.255
you're the other woman.

36:00.775 --> 36:01.896
How could she hit me?

36:03.615 --> 36:04.695
Xu Yan, stop right there!

36:09.775 --> 36:10.976
She's right.

36:13.056 --> 36:14.376
Who said we're divorced?

36:17.416 --> 36:20.056
Couples quarrel sometimes, okay?

36:20.416 --> 36:24.295
You're the Fang family heiress.
You can't be the other woman.

36:25.255 --> 36:26.336
Think carefully.

36:27.775 --> 36:28.735
Stop bothering me.

37:16.456 --> 37:16.976
Yan,

37:18.695 --> 37:20.896
there've been rumors lately

37:21.536 --> 37:24.336
that you and Mr. Shen
are getting a divorce.

37:25.536 --> 37:27.416
Everyone's buzzing about it.

37:27.735 --> 37:30.056
Even the management
are discreetly asking.

37:31.336 --> 37:32.295
I'm sure

37:32.735 --> 37:34.856
Sun Siwei started these rumors.

37:35.775 --> 37:36.655
But Yan,

37:37.295 --> 37:39.936
