37:40.295 --> 37:42.456
was practically confirmed.

37:42.976 --> 37:45.936
Now suddenly they favor Sun Siwei

37:46.456 --> 37:48.816
and start the restructuring

37:48.896 --> 37:50.496
to cut some shows.

37:50.856 --> 37:54.095
Family Feast's sponsors
are meddling too.

37:56.856 --> 38:00.655
I heard they secretly contacted
Sun Siwei's team.

38:03.016 --> 38:03.536
Yan,

38:06.416 --> 38:07.295
really divorced?

38:10.416 --> 38:11.695
You scared me.

38:11.816 --> 38:12.655
I knew it.

38:12.735 --> 38:13.775
You two were so close.

38:13.775 --> 38:14.615
How's this possible?

38:15.215 --> 38:18.775
But occasional arguments
between couples are normal, right?

38:20.095 --> 38:21.095
Don't worry about it.

38:21.936 --> 38:22.735
Go back to work.

38:23.135 --> 38:23.655
Alright.

38:23.816 --> 38:24.856
I'll get back to work.

38:26.255 --> 38:26.816
But listen,

38:27.536 --> 38:29.215
handle any issues properly.

38:29.376 --> 38:30.496
Don't act impulsively.

38:32.575 --> 38:33.735
Xu Yan, the star host.

39:12.095 --> 39:13.536
Aren't you working today?

39:17.095 --> 39:18.095
You saw me?

39:21.695 --> 39:23.175
I'm just concerned about you.

39:23.416 --> 39:25.016
After you secured the host position,

39:25.056 --> 39:27.175
I was going to buy flowers to celebrate.

39:27.735 --> 39:28.655
But look what happened.

39:29.336 --> 39:32.095
News about your divorce
is spreading everywhere.

39:33.135 --> 39:34.496
The situation looks bad.

39:35.056 --> 39:36.896
You never fix your issues.

39:39.735 --> 39:41.215
I've told you countless times.

39:43.496 --> 39:45.536
Focus on your own work.

39:46.936 --> 39:48.016
Then it won't be like this.

39:49.376 --> 39:50.615
Such a hypocrite.

39:50.735 --> 39:52.135
Focus on yourself?

39:53.016 --> 39:55.056
You really think your hosting skills

39:55.175 --> 39:58.016
made others concede defeat?

40:04.735 --> 40:05.816
I don't know if they

40:05.816 --> 40:06.655
concede defeat.

40:09.376 --> 40:09.976
But you...

40:23.775 --> 40:25.816
You used your husband's connections

40:25.856 --> 40:28.456
