40:54.775 --> 40:57.255
What's truly yours?

41:41.095 --> 41:41.775
Hello?

41:42.735 --> 41:44.695
Xu Yan, come to my office.

41:48.336 --> 41:48.936
Okay.

41:51.416 --> 41:51.936
Xu Yan,

41:52.856 --> 41:53.976
