42:09.175 --> 42:10.295
Your marriage really...

42:10.816 --> 42:12.016
Nothing to do with my husband.

42:16.255 --> 42:22.336
I'm just tired.

42:38.496 --> 42:40.936
(The key is controlling the heat.)

42:41.175 --> 42:43.095
(Oil temperature matters too.)

42:43.215 --> 42:44.896
(Should beef use higher heat?)

42:46.056 --> 42:47.695
(It depends on the cut.)

42:49.456 --> 42:50.016
(You also...)

42:50.016 --> 42:51.735
